rComments: Prof. Donar is the best! I have been able to improve by graphic design skills immensely under her guidance. Her feedback is actually helpful and she will work with you, as long as you show enthusiasm for the material.
Very kind and seems to genuinely care for students.
She's one of the nicest profs I have had in the CCIT program. Very clear with her material and is always willing to help students in class or by email (replies almost instantly).
She's very nice. Take all her classes. Her classes are the best and most useful compared to all CCT/VCC courses. :)

best cct prof! super helpful, send her drafts of your work and she'll give you tons of feedback. really wants her students to do well and a 4.0 is definitely attainable because the course content in 204 and 305 is very digestable. take her classes!
unhelpful, very dry in the way she communicates with students
